      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $X$ une variable aléatoire de loi de Poisson $\\mathcal{P}(\\lambda)$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X\\)</span> une variable aléatoire de loi de Poisson <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathcal{P}(\\lambda)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "cd3a7e1b-ad1d-4762-a760-2898c18b40a3",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer la fonction génératrice de $X$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer la fonction génératrice de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "e76ddfb2-23d2-4960-adeb-369accf8d684",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$G_X(z)=e^{\\lambda(z-1)}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(G_X(z)=e^{\\lambda(z-1)}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "50a9afe9-9fd1-440a-a215-79ad3e807cc9",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $E(X)$ et $\\text{Var}(X)$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(E(X)\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\text{Var}(X)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ce2db988-7868-4fa6-af77-292f5a1caf59",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$E(X)=\\text{Var}(X)=\\lambda$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(E(X)=\\text{Var}(X)=\\lambda\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6e74f313-c8e4-4e3a-bb23-8df37f801f59",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $Y$ une variable aléatoire de loi de Poisson $\\mathcal{P}(\\lambda')$, indépendante\nde $X$. Quelle est la loi de $X+Y$ ? En déduire que\n$\\mathcal{P}(\\lambda) *\\mathcal{P}(\\lambda')=\\mathcal{P}(\\lambda+\\lambda')$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(Y\\)</span> une variable aléatoire de loi de Poisson <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathcal{P}(\\lambda&#39;)\\)</span>, indépendante de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X\\)</span>. Quelle est la loi de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X+Y\\)</span> ? En déduire que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathcal{P}(\\lambda) *\\mathcal{P}(\\lambda&#39;)=\\mathcal{P}(\\lambda+\\lambda&#39;)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "8ac05ed1-b851-4892-beb4-69e6257a7830",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$G_{X+Y}(z)=G_X(z)G_Y(z)=e^{(\\lambda+\\lambda')(z-1)}$.\nD'où $X+Y\\sim \\mathcal{P}(\\lambda+\\lambda')$, et donc\n$\\mathcal{P}(\\lambda) *\\mathcal{P}(\\lambda')=\\mathcal{P}(\\lambda+\\lambda')$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(G_{X+Y}(z)=G_X(z)G_Y(z)=e^{(\\lambda+\\lambda&#39;)(z-1)}\\)</span>. D’où <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X+Y\\sim \\mathcal{P}(\\lambda+\\lambda&#39;)\\)</span>, et donc <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathcal{P}(\\lambda) *\\mathcal{P}(\\lambda&#39;)=\\mathcal{P}(\\lambda+\\lambda&#39;)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ],
